haggling in a central asian bazaar over the price 
of strawberries sparked a spasm of ethnic violence arson attacks 
and rampages by axwielding mobs in which 50 people were killed 
uzbekistans communist party chief reported tuesday 
rafik nishanov told lawmakers in moscow that authorities had 
