cents a pound feeder cattle were 25 cent lower to 13 cent higher 
with august at 7920 cents a pound hogs were 15 cent to 30 cent 
lower with june at 4845 cents a pound pork bellies were 30 cent 
to 1 cent lower with july at 3155 cents a pound 
